Text: Verify QUAD TEMP > 120 deg For At Least 25 min
CDR ACA (Deflect Slowly To Soft Stop, Pause At Null)
Possible QUAD Flags & RCS TCA Warn Lts - On
cb STAB/CONT: ATT DIR CONT - close
CDR ACA (Deflect Hardover, Pause At Null)
Possible QUAD Flags & RCS TCA Warn Lts - On
cb RCS SYS A: QUAD 4 TCA - close
cb RCS SYS A: QUAD 3 TCA - close
cb RCS SYS A: QUAD 2 TCA - close
cb RCS SYS A: QUAD 1 TCA - close
cb RCS SYS B: QUAD 1 TCA - close
cb RCS SYS B: QUAD 2 TCA - close
cb RCS SYS B: QUAD 3 TCA - close
cb RCS SYS B: QUAD 4 TCA - close
A = 1 If First Powerup, 0 If Second Powerup
